title: Lamar Jackson leads Russell Wilson in MVP Race, 2020 Mock Draft: Tua slips from 1st (Football 11/20)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Brady Quinn and Ryan Wilson to discuss the MVP race and if Lamar Jackson or Russell Wilson is in a better position to win (1:45), why Tom Brady is frustrated with the Patriots' offense (14:15), Philip Rivers' future (19:45), Rob Gronkowski's future (29:45) and how Tua Tagovailoa's injury impacts the 2020 NFL Draft (34:15) before answering 5-star reviews from Apple Podcasts (46:15)
